    "description": "SendEmailCore is a simple command line SMTP email client built in dotnet core. \n    This command requires two thing: 1. A from address. 2. A message. The message can be provided with either the -m command or piped in via STDIN.\n    Usage examples can be found at https://github.com/MrOnosa/SendEmailCore."
